Max Palmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Max_Palmer 0 Max Edmund Palmer (November 27, 1927 – May 7, 1984) was an American actor and professional wrestler. Known for his great height, in 2014 he was described as the second tallest professional wrestler in history.
